This paper deals with natural language processing and topic modeling, which are typically covered in the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the paper focuses on analyzing clinical reports, which could fall under the sub-category of cybernetics (cs.CY) as it involves the study of communication and control in biological systems.
